 1302                                                       ;If line inputted did not contain RUN or SCRatch com-
 1303                                                       ;mand, program continues by testing for SAVE or LOAD
 1304                                                       ;commands. If it does not find either of these com-
 1305                                                       ;mands, then operator did not input an executive com-
 1306                                                       ;mand. Program then sets up to see if the first entry in
 1307                                                       ;the line inputted is a LINE NUMBER.
 1308                     
 1309  0826  11 78 00     NOSCR:	LXI D,KW_SAVE                   ;Load DE with address of SAVE in look up table
